HOW TO FLASH THE POWER BOARD
============================

* Install arm-none-eabi toolchain (Ubuntu: sudo apt-get install arm-none-eabi-gcc)
* Install stm32flash (Ubuntu: sudo apt-get install stm32flash)
* Recursively init/update all submodules (git submodule --recursive --init update)
* cd libopencm3
* make
* cd ../dfu-bootloader/libopencm3
* make
* cd ../..
* make
* Connect a 3.3V USB-to-6-pin-UART cable (though 5V won't break the board, it's also not recommended)
* Flash pbv4.bin to the power board:
** stm32flash -b 115200 -w pbv4.bin /dev/ttyUSB0
